race.comment: INTREPID BALE (7) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fifth (29.66) in a Special conditions race at Sandown. Form at the trip sound including seven wins. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Key runner on his best form. SHE'S WIRED (2) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing third behind Canya Mayhem (30.13) in a Grade 4/5. Has the pace to be prominent. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Must be included in calculations. PANADERO RUBY (8) missed the frame last time when fourth (30.11) at Sandown but prior to that had three placings in a row. Form at the trip sound including two wins. The form from her last run stacks up well. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. PAPA EASY (1) scored in impressive time last start. Must include.
